---
const cards = [
  {
    title: 'No outsourcing',
    body: "Your code is written by experienced, US-based developers. Not farmed overseas and white-labeled back.",
  },
  {
    title: 'Embedded, not transactional',
    body: 'We learn your brand, your stack, your goals. The longer we work together, the more value we deliver.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Strategy + execution',
    body: 'Ecommerce consulting and development from the same team. No telephone game between strategist and dev.',
  },
];
---

<section class="bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-site mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="bg-charcoal rounded-2xl px-8 py-14 md:px-14 md:py-16">
      <h2
        class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-[40px] leading-[1.15] text-cream mb-6"
        data-sal="fade-up"
        data-sal-duration="500"
      >
        Fewer clients. Better results.
      </h2>

      <p
        class="text-[17px] leading-[1.8] text-white/55 max-w-[680px] mb-4"
        data-sal="fade-up"
        data-sal-duration="500"
        data-sal-delay="100"
      >
        Most agencies spread thin across dozens of projects. You get a junior
        dev, slow updates, and nobody who really understands your business. We do
        the opposite.
      </p>

      <p
        class="text-[17px] leading-[1.8] text-white/55 max-w-[680px] mb-10"
        data-sal="fade-up"
        data-sal-duration="500"
        data-sal-delay="200"
      >
        We work with a small number of brands at a time â€” going deep rather than
        wide. That means we understand your customers, your goals, and the
        metrics that matter. Not just shipping tickets, but thinking about what
        to build next and why.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {cards.map((card, i) => (
          <div
            class="bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.08] rounded-xl p-7"
            data-sal="fade-up"
            data-sal-duration="500"
            data-sal-delay={String(300 + i * 100)}
          >
            <h3 class="text-[15px] font-bold text-cream mb-2">{card.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/50">{card.body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
